CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 26, 2007

[Cite as 11/26/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-6205.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2007-1918. Disciplinary Counsel v. McShane.

On November 20, 2007, respondent filed a motion to remand this matter to the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline. In order to allow time for relator’s response and consideration of the motion by the court,

It is ordered, sua sponte, that the filing of objections is stayed until further order of this court.
